---
title: Cal Smart Harissa Double Shrimp and Chickpea Stew with Buttered Ciabatta
description: Smoky and complex North African spices are combined with chili-garlic sauce to infuse this dish with intense flavours. Ciabatta points are perfect dippers for this visually appealing and wholesome stew!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cal-smart-harissa-double-shrimp-and-chickpea-stew-faa09193.jpg
